## Verification

### List All OUs

```powershell
Get-ADOrganizationalUnit -Filter "Name -like '*'"
```

**Returns:** Staff, IT_Admins

### List Users in Staff OU

```powershell
Get-ADUser -Filter "Name -like '*'" -SearchBase "OU=Staff,DC=corp,DC=local"
```

**Returns:** jsmith, ajones, bwilson with full details

### List Group Members

```powershell
Get-ADGroupMember -Identity "Domain_Staff"
```

**Returns:** All three users with their details

